Evaṃ vutte thullanandā bhikkhunī taṃ purisaṃ etadavoca – ‘‘māyyo, evaṃ avaca, tumhākaṃ pitunā bhikkhunisaṅghassa dinno’’ti. ‘‘Dinno na dinno’’ti vohārike mahāmatte pucchiṃsu. Mahāmattā evamāhaṃsu – ‘‘ko, ayye, jānāti bhikkhunisaṅghassa dinno’’ti? Evaṃ vutte thullanandā bhikkhunī te mahāmatte etadavoca – ‘‘api nāyyo 
